{"id":11236,"date":"2020-08-24T15:47:33","date_gmt":"2020-08-24T15:47:33","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/fabeat.in\/?p=11236"},"modified":"2020-08-25T22:39:06","modified_gmt":"2020-08-25T22:39:06","slug":"top-5-drinks-to-consume-this-season-to-build-your-immunity","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/top-5-drinks-to-consume-this-season-to-build-your-immunity\/","title":{"rendered":"Top 5 Drinks To Consume This Season To Build Your Immunity"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"11714\" data-full-url=\"http:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9.jpg\" data-link=\"http:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/top-5-drinks-to-consume-this-season-to-build-your-immunity\/attachment\/9\/\" class=\"wp-image-11714\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-360x360.jpg 360w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-24x24.jpg 24w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-48x48.jpg 48w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-96x96.jpg 96w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-50x50.jpg 50w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-140x140.jpg 140w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-110x110.jpg 110w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-275x275.jpg 275w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-800x800.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9-550x550.jpg 550w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/9.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With the ongoing COVID-19 issue, strengthening our immunity system is the only way to keep the virus at bay and be confident enough to overcome the viral infection even if you are affected by it. Here are our top five recommendations that are really easy to prepare and yummy to drink when it comes to liquids you can consume to boost your immunity.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Spicy lemonade<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Ingredients:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>4 cups water<\/li><li>Lemon juice of one medium sized lemon<\/li><li>Few gratings of ginger<\/li><li>2-3&nbsp; chopped garlic cloves<\/li><li>1 cinnamon stick<\/li><li>Few mint leaves<\/li><li>1-2 tbsp. organic honey, to taste<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4>Method:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Add all the ingredients except honey to water and bring to a boil. Strain the mixture and add honey and consume warm.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Spiced tea<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Ingredients:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Peppercorns \u2013 2-3<\/li><li>Cloves \u2013 2-3<\/li><li>Ginger grated \u2013 1 tbsp<\/li><li>Cinnamon \u2013 1stick<\/li><li>Crushed cardamom \u2013 1-2<\/li><li>Star anise \u2013 1<\/li><li>Few tulsi leaves<\/li><li>Honey to taste<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4>Method:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Boil all the ingredients together for 25-30 minutes without honey. Strain and consume lukewarm with honey.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Spicy turmeric-milk drink<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Ingredients:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>1 tsp freshly grated turmeric<\/li><li>\u00bd tsp grated ginger<\/li><li>1.5-2 cups of soy\/almond milk<\/li><li>\u00bd cup coconut milk<\/li><li>&nbsp;1 cinnamon stick<\/li><li>2-3 tbsp honey<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4>Method:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Lightly heat all the ingredients except honey for 8-10 minutes without bringing to boil. Strain and serve warm adding the required amount of honey.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Green smoothie<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Ingredients:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>1 cup of baby spinach<\/li><li>\u00bd cup of cucumber<\/li><li>1 cup of curds<\/li><li>&nbsp;\u00bd tsp lemon juice<\/li><li>1-2 cups ice cubes<\/li><li>Few mint leaves<\/li><li>Salt to taste<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h4>Method:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Blend all the ingredients together until smooth and consume immediately.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Turmeric-Ginger chai<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11717\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-360x360.jpg 360w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-24x24.jpg 24w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-48x48.jpg 48w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-96x96.jpg 96w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-50x50.jpg 50w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-140x140.jpg 140w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-110x110.jpg 110w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-275x275.jpg 275w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-800x800.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1-550x550.jpg 550w, https:\/\/www.fabeat.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/7-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingredients:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Water- 3 cups<\/li><li>Fresh turmeric grated 1-2 tsp<\/li><li>Grated ginger- 1 tsp<\/li><li>Lemon juice 1 tbsp<\/li><li>Honey to taste<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Method:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Boil turmeric and ginger in water for 12-15 minutes, strain and add lemon juice. Serve warm with honey.&nbsp;<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.inspiringquotes.us\/quotes\/sFjG_p1jYqWK5\">No doctor has ever healed anyone of anything in the history of the world, The human immune system heals and that&#8217;s the only thing that heals<\/a><\/p><p><\/p><cite><strong>Bo<\/strong>b Wright<\/cite><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-0 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery alignwide columns-0 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"> <em> <\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>With the ongoing COVID-19 issue, strengthening our immunity system is the only way to keep the virus at bay and be confident enough to overcome the viral infection even if you are affected by it. Here 